{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775880959931,"sessionID":"ses_2854178afffe40mg2XimqIneGs","part":{"id":"prt_d7abef8fc001wfGqf5e2nwqbtM","messageID":"msg_d7abed40e001ncpe9RJdm5fUTF","sessionID":"ses_2854178afffe40mg2XimqIneGs","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_12482a11d67246a29ee07883","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore client-go codebase","prompt":"Thoroughly explore the client-go directory in /home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/client-go/. Read ALL Go files to understand:\n\n1. The complete package structure and what already exists\n2. What CRD types are defined (look for AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter, etc.)\n3. What clientset, typed clients, informers, and listers already exist\n4. What interfaces are defined\n5. The Go module name and dependencies\n\nAlso search for any \"ST-3\" or \"AR-035\" references anywhere in the project.\n\nAlso read the go.mod file at the project root.\n\nAlso look for any pkg/apis or api definitions that define the CRD types.\n\nReturn a comprehensive summary of:\n- All existing files and their contents (summarize each)\n- What CRD types exist\n- What's already implemented vs what's missing\n- The Go module path\n- Any references to ST-3 or AR-035","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_28540f502ffev1bdGp7teMLPOI (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nNow I have a complete picture. Here is the comprehensive summary:\n\n---\n\n## Comprehensive Summary\n\n### 1. Go Module Path and Dependencies\n\n**Module path:** `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`\n\n**Go version:** 1.25.0\n\n**Key direct dependencies:**\n- `k8s.io/api v0.34.1`\n- `k8s.io/apimachinery v0.34.1`\n- `k8s.io/client-go v0.34.1`\n- `k8s.io/klog/v2 v2.130.1`\n- `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime v0.22.2`\n- `github.com/gin-gonic/gin v1.10.0`\n- `github.com/redis/go-redis/v9 v9.18.0`\n- `github.com/prometheus/client_golang v1.22.0`\n\n**Note:** There is NO separate `go.mod` inside the `client-go/` directory. It is a subpackage of the root module.\n\n---\n\n### 2. CRD Types Defined\n\nThere are **two API groups** with CRD types:\n\n#### API Group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\nLocated at: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n\n| Type | Plural | Scope | Subresources |\n|------|--------|-------|--------------|\n| **AgentRuntime** | `agentruntimes` | Namespaced | `/status` |\n| **AgentRuntimeList** | (list type) | -- | -- |\n| **CodeInterpreter** | `codeinterpreters` | Namespaced | `/status` |\n| **CodeInterpreterList** | (list type) | -- | -- |\n\n**AgentRuntime** fields:\n- `Spec.Ports` ([]TargetPort)\n- `Spec.Template` (*SandboxTemplate -- wraps corev1.PodSpec with labels/annotations)\n- `Spec.SessionTimeout` (*metav1.Duration)\n- `Spec.MaxSessionDuration` (*metav1.Duration)\n- `Status.Conditions` ([]metav1.Condition)\n\n**CodeInterpreter** fields:\n- `Spec.Ports` ([]TargetPort)\n- `Spec.Template` (*CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate -- has Image, ImagePullPolicy, Resources, Environment, Command, Args, RuntimeClassName, etc.)\n- `Spec.SessionTimeout` (*metav1.Duration)\n- `Spec.MaxSessionDuration` (*metav1.Duration)\n- `Spec.WarmPoolSize` (*int32)\n- `Spec.AuthMode` (AuthModeType: \"picod\" or \"none\")\n- `Status.Conditions` ([]metav1.Condition)\n- `Status.Ready` (bool)\n\n**Shared types:**\n- `TargetPort` -- {PathPrefix, Name, Port, Protocol}\n- `ProtocolType` -- \"HTTP\" or \"HTTPS\"\n- `AuthModeType` -- \"picod\" or \"none\"\n\n#### API Group: `agents.x-k8s.io/v1alpha1`\nLocated at: `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/agents/v1alpha1/`\n\n| Type | Plural | Subresources |\n|------|--------|--------------|\n| **Sandbox** | (not specified) | `/status` |\n| **SandboxList** | (list type) | -- |\n\n**Sandbox** fields:\n- `Spec.Image` (string)\n- `Spec.Command` (string)\n- `Status.Phase` (string)\n\n---\n\n### 3. Complete File Inventory in `client-go/` (10 files total)\n\n#### Clientset Layer (4 files)\n\n| File | Path | Summary |\n|------|------|---------|\n| **clientset.go** | `client-go/clientset/clientset.go` | Defines `Interface` with one method: `RuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface`. Minimal -- no Discovery client. |\n| **real.go** | `client-go/clientset/real.go` | Defines `Clientset` struct with `runtimeV1alpha1` field. Has `NewForConfig(cfg *rest.Config)` that returns an empty `&Clientset{}` (stub -- does not initialize the typed client). Implements `RuntimeV1alpha1()` accessor. |\n| **fake.go** | `client-go/clientset/fake.go` | Defines `FakeClientset` with `agentRuntimeStore`, `codeInterpreterStore`, and `runtimeClient`. `NewFakeClientset()` creates ObjectStores for both `agentruntimes` and `codeinterpreters` resources and wires them to a `RuntimeV1alpha1Client`. Provides `GetAgentRuntimeStore()` and `GetCodeInterpreterStore()` accessors. |\n\n#### Typed Client Layer (3 files)\n\n| File | Path | Summary |\n|------|------|---------|\n| **interfaces.go** | `client-go/clientset/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/interfaces.go` | Defines three interfaces: `AgentRuntimeInterface` (8 methods: Create, Update, UpdateStatus, Delete, Get, List, Watch, Patch), `CodeInterpreterInterface` (same 8 methods), and `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` (AgentRuntimes(ns), CodeInterpreters(ns)). |\n| **runtime_client.go** | `client-go/clientset/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go` | Contains: (1) `ObjectStore` -- an in-memory thread-safe store for fake clients with Get/Create/Update/Delete/List operations. (2) `AgentRuntimeClient` -- implements `AgentRuntimeInterface` backed by ObjectStore. (3) `CodeInterpreterClient` -- implements `CodeInterpreterInterface` backed by ObjectStore. Both implement full CRUD + Watch (fake) + Patch (no-op read). |\n| **client.go** | `client-go/clientset/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/client.go` | Defines `RuntimeV1alpha1Client` struct with stores for both resource types. `NewRuntimeV1alpha1Client()` constructor. `AgentRuntimes(ns)` and `CodeInterpreters(ns)` methods return typed clients. Also defines `agentRuntimeGVR` and `codeInterpreterGVR` variables. |\n\n#### Informer Layer (3 files)\n\n| File | Path | Summary |\n|------|------|---------|\n| **factory.go** | `client-go/informers/externalversions/factory.go` | Defines `SharedInformerFactory` interface (Start, Shutdown, WaitForCacheSync, Runtime) and `sharedInformerFactory` struct. Has two constructors: `NewSharedInformerFactory(cs, resync)` and `NewSharedInformerFactoryFromReal(factory)`. The fake path is a stub (Start/Shutdown/WaitForCacheSync are mostly no-ops or delegate to realFactory). `Runtime()` returns `runtime.New()`. |\n| **runtime/interface.go** | `client-go/informers/externalversions/runtime/interface.go` | Defines group-level `Interface` with `V1alpha1()` method. `runtime` struct implements it. `New()` returns the struct. |\n| **runtime/v1alpha1/interface.go** | `client-go/informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/interface.go` | Defines version-level `Interface` with `AgentRuntimes()` and `CodeInterpreters()` methods. Also defines `AgentRuntimeInformer` and `CodeInterpreterInformer` interfaces (each with `Informer()` and `Lister()`). Concrete implementations `agentRuntimeInformer` and `codeInterpreterInformer` create `cache.NewSharedIndexInformer` with empty `&cache.ListWatch{}` and 30s resync. |\n\n#### Lister Layer (1 file)\n\n| File | Path | Summary |\n|------|------|---------|\n| **expansion_generated.go** | `client-go/listers/runtime/v1alpha1/expansion_generated.go` | Defines `AgentRuntimeLister` interface (List, AgentRuntimes(ns)), `AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister` (List, Get), `CodeInterpreterLister` (List, CodeInterpreters(ns)), `CodeInterpreterNamespaceLister` (List, Get). Also has concrete implementations `agentRuntimeLister`, `agentRuntimeNamespaceLister`, `codeInterpreterLister`, `codeInterpreterNamespaceLister` backed by `cache.Indexer`. |\n\n---\n\n### 4. What Is Already Implemented vs. What Is Missing\n\n#### Implemented (stub/in-memory versions):\n- Clientset `Interface` with `RuntimeV1alpha1()` accessor\n- `Clientset` struct with `NewForConfig()` (stub -- returns empty struct)\n- `FakeClientset` with ObjectStore-backed fake clients for both AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter\n- `AgentRuntimeInterface` and `CodeInterpreterInterface` with full CRUD + Watch + Patch signatures\n- `RuntimeV1alpha1Client` with `AgentRuntimes(ns)` and `CodeInterpreters(ns)` accessors\n- `ObjectStore` -- thread-safe in-memory store for fake clients\n- `SharedInformerFactory` interface and basic struct\n- Group and version informer accessors (`Runtime()`, `V1alpha1()`)\n- `AgentRuntimeInformer` and `CodeInterpreterInformer` with `Informer()` and `Lister()` methods\n- `AgentRuntimeLister`, `AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister`, `CodeInterpreterLister`, `CodeInterpreterNamespaceLister` with full implementations\n- Expansion interfaces for listers\n\n#### Missing (compared to the delta-spec requirements):\n1. **Clientset:**\n   - No `Discovery()` method on `Interface`\n   - No `NewForConfigAndClient()` constructor\n   - No `NewForConfigOrDie()` constructor\n   - No `New(rest.Interface)` constructor\n   - `NewForConfig()` does not actually initialize the typed client (returns empty struct)\n   - No `*discovery.DiscoveryClient` embedding\n\n2. **Typed Client:**\n   - No `RESTClient() rest.Interface` method on `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface`\n   - No `AgentRuntimesGetter` or `CodeInterpretersGetter` separate interfaces\n   - No `DeleteCollection` method on either typed client\n   - No real REST-based implementation (all backed by in-memory ObjectStore)\n   - No `generated_expansion.go` with `AgentRuntimeExpansion` / `CodeInterpreterExpansion` empty interfaces\n   - No `doc.go` files\n   - No `scheme/register.go` for the clientset\n\n3. **Informers:**\n   - No `generic.go` with `GenericInformer` and `ForResource()` routing\n   - No `internalinterfaces/factory_interfaces.go` with `NewInformerFunc`, `TweakListOptionsFunc`, `SharedInformerFactory` base interface\n   - No `NewAgentRuntimeInformer()` / `NewCodeInterpreterInformer()` standalone constructors\n   - No `NewFilteredAgentRuntimeInformer()` / `NewFilteredCodeInterpreterInformer()`\n   - No `InformerFor()` method on factory\n   - No `ForResource()` method on factory\n   - Informers use empty `&cache.ListWatch{}` (no actual list/watch functions wired)\n   - Factory `Start()` is a no-op for the fake path\n\n4. **Listers:**\n   - No separate `agentruntime.go` and `codeinterpreter.go` files (all in one `expansion_generated.go`)\n   - No `AgentRuntimeListerExpansion`, `AgentRuntimeNamespaceListerExpansion`, `CodeInterpreterListerExpansion`, `CodeInterpreterNamespaceListerExpansion` empty expansion interfaces\n   - No `GroupResource` used for error reporting in listers\n\n5. **Fake Clients:**\n   - No `fake/` subdirectory under `clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n   - No `*testing.Fake`-based fake implementations\n   - No `NewSimpleClientset(objects...)` constructor\n   - No fake `register.go`\n\n6. **Build/Generation:**\n   - No `Makefile` with `gen-client` target\n   - No `hack/update-codegen.sh` script\n   - No code-generator integration\n\n7. **Test files:**\n   - No `*_test.go` files anywhere in the `client-go/` directory\n\n---\n\n### 5. ST-3 and AR-035 References\n\n**AR-035** is the change request for \"client-go type client generation\" (client-go 类型客户端生成). It is referenced in:\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-035/design.md` -- Full design document with detailed requirements for Clientset, Typed Clients, Informers, Listers, Fake Clients, Scheme, and regeneration.\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-035/delta-spec.md` -- Detailed Gherkin-style scenarios for every requirement. Lists 26 files that should exist after code generation.\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-035/proposal.md` -- Proposal document.\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-035/tasks.md` -- Task tracking (mostly TODO placeholders).\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/.sdd_prompt.md` -- References \"AR: AR-035 -- client-go 类型客户端生成\"\n\n**ST-3** refers to \"Stage ST-3 (Design)\" or \"Stage ST-3 (Design Complete)\". It is referenced as a precondition in the tasks.md files for AR-002 through AR-035 (every change request). Specifically in AR-035's tasks.md: `Precondition: Stage ST-3 (Design) completed`.\n\n---\n\n### 6. Directory Structure Summary\n\n```\nclient-go/\n  clientset/\n    clientset.go              -- Interface definition\n    real.go                   -- Real Clientset (stub)\n    fake.go                   -- FakeClientset with ObjectStores\n    typed/runtime/v1alpha1/\n      interfaces.go           -- AgentRuntimeInterface, CodeInterpreterInterface, RuntimeV1alpha1Interface\n      runtime_client.go       -- ObjectStore + AgentRuntimeClient + CodeInterpreterClient (in-memory)\n      client.go               -- RuntimeV1alpha1Client + GVRs\n  informers/\n    externalversions/\n      factory.go              -- SharedInformerFactory\n      runtime/\n        interface.go          -- Group-level Interface\n        v1alpha1/\n          interface.go        -- Version-level Interface + informer implementations\n  listers/\n    runtime/v1alpha1/\n      expansion_generated.go  -- All lister interfaces + implementations\n\npkg/apis/\n  runtime/v1alpha1/\n    agent_type.go             -- AgentRuntime CRD type\n    codeinterpreter_types.go  -- CodeInterpreter CRD type\n    shared_types.go           -- TargetPort, ProtocolType, AuthModeType\n    groupversion_info.go      -- GroupVersion, SchemeBuilder, Kind constants\n    constants.go              -- Annotation constants\n    doc.go                    -- Codegen markers\n    zz_generated.deepcopy.go  -- DeepCopy methods\n    *_test.go                 -- Unit tests\n  agents/v1alpha1/\n    sandbox_types.go          -- Sandbox CRD type (separate API group)\n    zz_generated.deepcopy.go  -- DeepCopy methods\n```\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_28540f502ffev1bdGp7teMLPOI","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore client-go codebase","time":{"start":1775880833786,"end":1775880959927}}}}
