{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775881125805,"sessionID":"ses_2854178afffe40mg2XimqIneGs","part":{"id":"prt_d7ac20373001nxva6tkkTfgu78","messageID":"msg_d7ac1dc23001WDlfB0UBuyURD1","sessionID":"ses_2854178afffe40mg2XimqIneGs","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_9ecec4e0efd145e2a7266f7f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# AR-035 — client-go 类型客户端生成 — Tasks\n\n> **Module:** client-go\n> **Language:** Go\n> **Size:** L\n> **Precondition:** Stage ST-3 (Design) completed\n> **Reference:** `changes/AR-035/proposal.md`, `changes/AR-035/design.md`, `changes/AR-035/delta-spec.md`\n> **Dependency:** `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` types with `+genclient` markers (already present), `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` (already present)\n\n---\n\n## T-001: 生成基础设施 — hack/update-codegen.sh + Makefile gen-client\n\n- [ ] Create `hack/boilerplate.go.txt` with standard Apache 2.0 header template\n- [ ] Create `hack/update-codegen.sh` script that:\n  - [ ] Uses `k8s.io/code-generator` v0.34.1 (downloaded via `go run k8s.io/code-generator/cmd/...` or `go install`)\n  - [ ] Runs `client-gen` → outputs to `client-go/clientset/versioned/`\n  - [ ] Runs `lister-gen` → outputs to `client-go/listers/`\n  - [ ] Runs `informer-gen` → outputs to `client-go/informers/`\n  - [ ] Uses `--with-watch` flag on all generators\n  - [ ] Sets `--output-package=github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`\n  - [ ] Sets `--input-base=github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis` and `--input=runtime/v1alpha1`\n  - [ ] Sets `--go-header-file=hack/boilerplate.go.txt`\n  - [ ] Is idempotent (can be re-run safely)\n- [ ] Add `gen-client` target to `Makefile` that invokes `hack/update-codegen.sh`\n- [ ] Add `gen-client` to `.PHONY` declaration\n- [ ] Verify `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go` has `// +k8s:deepcopy-gen=package` and `// +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- [ ] Verify `AgentRuntime` and `CodeInterpreter` types have `// +genclient` marker\n- [ ] Run `make gen-client` and verify it completes without error\n- [ ] Verify all 26 expected files are generated (see File Index in delta-spec.md)\n\n**验收**:\n```bash\nmake gen-client\ngo build ./client-go/...\n```\nNo compilation errors; all expected files exist under `client-go/`.\n\n---\n\n## T-002: Clientset 和 Typed REST Client 生成验证\n\n> Generated by T-001; this task verifies and validates the output.\n\n### Clientset (`client-go/clientset/versioned/clientset.go`)\n- [ ] `Interface` declares `Discovery() discovery.DiscoveryInterface` and `RuntimeV1alpha1() runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface`\n- [ ] `Clientset` struct embeds `*discovery.DiscoveryClient` and holds `runtimeV1alpha1 *runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Client`\n- [ ] `NewForConfig(c *rest.Config) (*Clientset, error)` creates clientset from `rest.Config`\n- [ ] `NewForConfigAndClient(c *rest.Config, httpClient *http.Client) (*Clientset, error)` uses custom HTTP client\n- [ ] `NewForConfigOrDie(c *rest.Config) *Clientset` panics on invalid config\n- [ ] `New(c rest.Interface) *Clientset` creates from pre-configured `rest.Interface`\n\n### Scheme (`client-go/clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go`)\n- [ ] `Scheme`, `Codecs`, `ParameterCodec` are package-level variables\n- [ ] `AddToScheme` registers `AgentRuntime`, `AgentRuntimeList`, `CodeInterpreter`, `CodeInterpreterList`\n\n### Typed Client (`client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/`)\n- [ ] `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` declares `RESTClient() rest.Interface`, `AgentRuntimesGetter`, `CodeInterpretersGetter`\n- [ ] `RuntimeV1alpha1Client` implements `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` with `rest.Interface`\n- [ ] `AgentRuntimesGetter` declares `AgentRuntimes(namespace string) AgentRuntimeInterface`\n- [ ] `CodeInterpretersGetter` declares `CodeInterpreters(namespace string) CodeInterpreterInterface`\n- [ ] `AgentRuntimeInterface` has all 9 CRUD methods: Create, Update, UpdateStatus, Delete, DeleteCollection, Get, List, Watch, Patch\n- [ ] `CodeInterpreterInterface` has all 9 CRUD methods with `CodeInterpreter` types\n- [ ] `AgentRuntime` resource plural is `agentruntimes`\n- [ ] `CodeInterpreter` resource plural is `codeinterpreters`\n- [ ] `generated_expansion.go` has empty `AgentRuntimeExpansion` and `CodeInterpreterExpansion` interfaces\n- [ ] `GroupVersion` is `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`, `APIPath` is `/apis`\n\n### Build verification\n- [ ] `go build ./client-go/clientset/...` compiles without errors\n- [ ] Compile-time interface check: `var _ versioned.Interface = &clientset.Clientset{}`\n- [ ] Compile-time interface check: `var _ runtimev1alpha1.RuntimeV1alpha1Interface = &clientset.RuntimeV1alpha1Client{}`\n- [ ] Compile-time interface check: `var _ runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntimeInterface = &clientset.AgentRuntime{}`\n- [ ] Compile-time interface check: `var _ runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreterInterface = &clientset.CodeInterpreter{}`\n\n**验收**:\n```bash\ngo build ./client-go/clientset/...\n```\n\n---\n\n## T-003: Fake Clients 生成验证\n\n> Generated by T-001; this task verifies and validates the fake client output.\n\n### Fake Typed Clients (`client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/`)\n- [ ] `FakeRuntimeV1alpha1` embeds `*testing.Fake` and implements `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface`\n- [ ] `FakeAgentRuntimes` implements `AgentRuntimeInterface` using `*testing.Fake` actions\n- [ ] `FakeCodeInterpreters` implements `CodeInterpreterInterface` using `*testing.Fake` actions\n\n### Fake Clientset (`client-go/clientset/versioned/fake/`)\n- [ ] `NewSimpleClientset(objects ...runtime.Object) *Clientset` creates fake clientset with initial objects\n- [ ] `NewClientset(client *restclient.RESTClient, objects ...runtime.Object) *Clientset` with custom REST client\n- [ ] Fake `Clientset` implements `versioned.Interface`\n- [ ] `fake/register.go` wires same scheme as real clientset\n\n### Fake behavior verification\n- [ ] `Get` non-existent resource → `apierrors.NewNotFound`\n- [ ] `Create` existing resource → `apierrors.NewAlreadyExists`\n- [ ] `Update` non-existent resource → `apierrors.NewNotFound`\n- [ ] `Delete` non-existent resource → `apierrors.NewNotFound`\n- [ ] `PrependReactor` can override default behavior\n\n**验收**:\n```bash\ngo build ./client-go/clientset/versioned/fake/...\ngo build ./client-go/clientset/versioned/typed/runtime/v1alpha1/fake/...\n```\n\n---\n\n## T-004: Informer Factory 生成验证\n\n> Generated by T-001; this task verifies and validates the informer output.\n\n### SharedInformerFactory (`informers/externalversions/factory.go`)\n- [ ] `SharedInformerFactory` interface embeds `internalinterfaces.SharedInformerFactory`\n- [ ] Declares `Start(stopCh <-chan struct{})`, `Shutdown()`, `WaitForCacheSync(stopCh) map[reflect.Type]bool`\n- [ ] Declares `ForResource(GVR) (GenericInformer, error)`, `InformerFor(obj, newFunc)`, `Runtime()`\n- [ ] `NewSharedInformerFactory(client, defaultResync)` constructor\n- [ ] `NewSharedInformerFactoryWithOptions(client, defaultResync, options...)` constructor\n- [ ] Options: `WithCustomResyncConfig`, `WithTweakListOptions`, `WithNamespace`, `WithTransform`\n\n### Generic informer (`informers/externalversions/generic.go`)\n- [ ] `GenericInformer` wraps `SharedIndexInformer` with `Informer()` and `Lister()` methods\n- [ ] `ForResource(agentruntimes GVR)` → returns `f.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes().Informer()`\n- [ ] `ForResource(codeinterpreters GVR)` → returns `f.Runtime().V1alpha1().CodeInterpreters().Informer()`\n- [ ] `ForResource(unknown GVR)` → returns `(nil, error)`\n\n### internalinterfaces (`informers/externalversions/internalinterfaces/factory_interfaces.go`)\n- [ ] `NewInformerFunc` = `func(versioned.Interface, time.Duration) cache.SharedIndexInformer`\n- [ ] `SharedInformerFactory` declares `Start(stopCh <-chan struct{})` and `InformerFor(obj, newFunc)`\n- [ ] `TweakListOptionsFunc` = `func(*metav1.ListOptions)`\n\n### Per-type informers (`informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/`)\n- [ ] `AgentRuntimeInformer` declares `Informer() cache.SharedIndexInformer` and `Lister() AgentRuntimeLister`\n- [ ] `CodeInterpreterInformer` declares `Informer() cache.SharedIndexInformer` and `Lister() CodeInterpreterLister`\n- [ ] `NewAgentRuntimeInformer(client, namespace, resync, indexers)` returns `cache.SharedIndexInformer`\n- [ ] `NewFilteredAgentRuntimeInformer(client, namespace, resync, indexers, tweakListOptions)` with filtered list options\n- [ ] `NewCodeInterpreterInformer(client, namespace, resync, indexers)` returns `cache.SharedIndexInformer`\n- [ ] `NewFilteredCodeInterpreterInformer(client, namespace, resync, indexers, tweakListOptions)` with filtered list options\n- [ ] Informers use real `cache.ListWatch` with List/Watch functions (not empty stubs)\n\n### Group/version accessors\n- [ ] `Runtime()` returns `externalversionsruntime.Interface` with `V1alpha1()` method\n- [ ] `V1alpha1()` returns interface with `AgentRuntimes()` and `CodeInterpreters()` accessors\n\n**验收**:\n```bash\ngo build ./client-go/informers/...\n```\n\n---\n\n## T-005: Listers 生成验证\n\n> Generated by T-001; this task verifies and validates the lister output.\n\n### AgentRuntime Lister (`listers/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go`)\n- [ ] `AgentRuntimeLister` declares `List(selector) ([]*AgentRuntime, error)`, `AgentRuntimes(namespace) AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister`, `AgentRuntimeListerExpansion`\n- [ ] `AgentRuntimeNamespaceLister` declares `List(selector) ([]*AgentRuntime, error)`, `Get(name) (*AgentRuntime, error)`, `AgentRuntimeNamespaceListerExpansion`\n- [ ] `NewAgentRuntimeLister(indexer)` uses `Resource(\"agentruntime\").GroupResource()` for error reporting\n\n### CodeInterpreter Lister (`listers/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go`)\n- [ ] `CodeInterpreterLister` declares `List`, `CodeInterpreters(namespace) CodeInterpreterNamespaceLister`, `CodeInterpreterListerExpansion`\n- [ ] `CodeInterpreterNamespaceLister` declares `List`, `Get`, `CodeInterpreterNamespaceListerExpansion`\n- [ ] `NewCodeInterpreterLister(indexer)` uses `Resource(\"codeinterpreter\").GroupResource()` for error reporting\n\n### Expansion interfaces (`listers/runtime/v1alpha1/expansion_generated.go`)\n- [ ] `AgentRuntimeListerExpansion` is empty interface\n- [ ] `AgentRuntimeNamespaceListerExpansion` is empty interface\n- [ ] `CodeInterpreterListerExpansion` is empty interface\n- [ ] `CodeInterpreterNamespaceListerExpansion` is empty interface\n\n**验收**:\n```bash\ngo build ./client-go/listers/...\n```\n\n---\n\n## T-006: 迁移 — 删除手写代码 + 更新消费者导入路径\n\n### 删除手写代码\n- [ ] Delete `client-go/clientset/clientset.go` (old hand-written Interface)\n- [ ] Delete `client-go/clientset/real.go` (old stub Clientset)\n- [ ] Delete `client-go/clientset/fake.go` (old ObjectStore-based FakeClientset)\n- [ ] Delete `client-go/clientset/typed/` (old typed clients backed by ObjectStore)\n- [ ] Delete `client-go/informers/externalversions/factory.go` (old stub factory)\n- [ ] Delete `client-go/informers/externalversions/runtime/interface.go` (old stub group accessor)\n- [ ] Delete `client-go/informers/externalversions/runtime/v1alpha1/interface.go` (old stub informers with empty ListWatch{})\n- [ ] Delete `client-go/listers/runtime/v1alpha1/expansion_generated.go` (old lister implementations)\n\n### 更新消费者导入路径\n- [ ] `cmd/router/main.go`: update `client-go/clientset` → `client-go/clientset/versioned`\n- [ ] `cmd/workloadmanager/main.go`: update `client-go/clientset` → `client-go/clientset/versioned`\n- [ ] `cmd/workloadmanager/main.go`: update `client-go/informers/externalversions` → new generated path\n- [ ] `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/reconciler.go`: update `client-go/clientset` → `client-go/clientset/versioned`\n- [ ] `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/reconciler.go`: update `client-go/informers/externalversions` → new generated path\n- [ ] `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/reconciler.go`: update `client-go/listers/runtime/v1alpha1` → new generated path\n- [ ] `pkg/workloadmanager/reconciler/types.go`: update `client-go/clientset` → `clie