me` registers `CodeInterpreterList` type\n- [ ] Test: fake scheme matches real scheme for type recognition\n\n### Fake Client CRUD 测试\n- [ ] Test: AgentRuntime Create → Get returns same object\n- [ ] Test: AgentRuntime Update → Get returns updated object\n- [ ] Test: AgentRuntime UpdateStatus → only status field changes, spec unchanged\n- [ ] Test: AgentRuntime Delete → subsequent Get returns NotFound\n- [ ] Test: AgentRuntime List returns all objects in namespace\n- [ ] Test: AgentRuntime DeleteCollection → subsequent List returns empty\n- [ ] Test: AgentRuntime Watch → receives ADDED event after Create\n- [ ] Test: AgentRuntime Patch → partial field update\n- [ ] Test: CodeInterpreter full CRUD lifecycle (same as AgentRuntime)\n- [ ] Test: Get non-existent → `apierrors.IsNotFound(err)` is true\n- [ ] Test: Create duplicate → `apierrors.IsAlreadyExists(err)` is true\n- [ ] Test: namespace isolation — resources in different namespaces don't interfere\n\n### Informer 集成测试\n- [ ] Test: `NewSharedInformerFactory(cs, 30s)` returns factory\n- [ ] Test: `factory.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes().Informer()` returns `SharedIndexInformer`\n- [ ] Test: `factory.Runtime().V1alpha1().AgentRuntimes().Lister()` returns `AgentRuntimeLister`\n- [ ] Test: `ForResource(agentruntimes GVR)` returns correct informer\n- [ ] Test: `ForResource(codeinterpreters GVR)` returns correct informer\n- [ ] Test: `ForResource(unknown GVR)` returns error\n\n### Lister 测试\n- [ ] Test: `lister.List(labels.Everything())` returns all objects\n- [ ] Test: `lister.AgentRuntimes(\"default\").Get(\"name\")` returns namespaced object\n- [ ] Test: `lister.AgentRuntimes(\"default\").Get(\"nonexistent\")` returns error\n\n### Clientset 构造函数测试\n- [ ] Test: `NewForConfigOrDie` with valid config returns without panic\n- [ ] Test: `New` with `rest.Interface` wires typed client correctly\n\n**验收**:\n```bash\ngo test ./client-go/... -v\n```\nAll tests pass.\n\n---\n\n## T-008: 文档 + 最终验证\n\n- [ ] Update `deploymen